JGoff-App-Perltidy

PPI-based replacement for App::Perltidy. Eventually this will have a companion
program that analyzes the indent style of your existing perl code and can feed
this application.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc JGoff::App::Perltidy

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=JGoff-App-Perltidy

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/JGoff-App-Perltidy

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/JGoff-App-Perltidy

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/JGoff-App-Perltidy/


